body_html:
I installed the latest Tensorflow whl file through pip and attempted to use tf.one_hot. Now I'm getting

tensorflow.python.framework.errors.InvalidArgumentError: No OpKernel was registered to support Op 'OneHot' with these attrs
     [[Node: OneHot = OneHot[T=DT_BOOL, axis=-1](ArgMax, OneHot/depth, OneHot/on_value, OneHot/off_value)]]

Did I do something wrong?
